      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 14.11 - 老子 14.12</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 14.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>是謂無狀之狀，無物之象，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>This is called the Form of the Formless, and the Semblance of the Invisible;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-014__align-006">
