      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">4</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 14.16 - 老子 14.19</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 14.9</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>執古之道，以御今之有。能知古始，是謂道紀。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When we can lay hold of the Dao of old to direct the things of the present day, and are able to know it as it was of old in the beginning, this is called (unwinding) the clue of Dao.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
